data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the desirable Forest Lake Community of Davenport, FL! This stunning 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom home, built in 2022, boasts modern elegance and smart living features. The spacious 2696 square feet offer a perfect blend of style and comfort.  Step into luxury with granite countertops, upgraded appliances, and soft-close cabinets in the kitchen. The living areas on the first floor are adorned with beautiful ceramic tiles, while the rooms feature cozy carpets. Blackout zebra blinds provide both style and functionality.  Upstairs, the primary suite awaits, complete with his and her closets and upgraded bathrooms. Enjoy the convenience of a dedicated laundry room with a Bluetooth washer and dryer, adding a tech-savvy touch to your daily chores.  Entertain guests in the loft or relax in the hot tub in the fenced-in backyard surrounded by beautiful pavers. This two-story home is equipped with fans, gutters, and an extended driveway for added convenience.  With ample storage and closets throughout, this home is designed to cater to your organizational needs. Embrace the lifestyle of a smart house with all the latest amenities.  Make your mark in Forest Lake with this exceptional home, where every detail has been carefully considered. Your comfort, convenience, and style converge seamlessly in this modern masterpiece. Don't miss the chance to call this two-story haven yours!  Schedule a showing today and let the journey to your new home begin. Because when it comes to finding the perfect home, you deserve nothing less than extraordinary. Welcome to your forever home - where luxury meets technology. "Home is where your story begins..."    In order to ensure the Buyer is aware of the new law restricting certain real estate purchases by certain Foreign Buyers, we request Buyer signatures on the Foreign Buyers Notice (available in the attachments), to accompany all offers.
